  "text": "The CUB-200-2011 dataset consists of 11, 788 images of 200 bird categories. Again we follow the evaluation protocol proposed in [CITATION_1] , using the first 100 classes consisting of 5, 864 images for training and the remaining 100 classes with 5, 924 images for testing.",
